<LinearLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    xmlns:cardview="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res-auto"
    android:background="#e9e9e9"
    android:orientation="vertical"
    android:layout_width="fill_parent"
    android:layout_height="fill_parent"
    android:gravity="center_horizontal"
    android:padding="5dp">

    <ScrollView
        android:id="@+id/card_scrollview"
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:fadeScrollbars="true"
        android:layout_height="match_parent" >

        <LinearLayout
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:orientation="vertical" >

            <android.support.v7.widget.CardView
                android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                cardview:cardUseCompatPadding="true"
                android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                cardview:cardElevation="4dp"
                cardview:cardCornerRadius="5dp">
                <LinearLayout
                    android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                    android:layout_height="30dp"
                    android:gravity="top"
                    android:background="@drawable/banner"
                    android:orientation="vertical"
                    android:padding="8dp"/>
                <LinearLayout
                    android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:orientation="vertical"
                    android:padding="8dp">
                    <ImageView
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="250dp"
                        android:id="@+id/imageView2"
                        android:src="@drawable/gdgminnaweb" />


                </LinearLayout>
            </android.support.v7.widget.CardView>

            <android.support.v7.widget.CardView
                android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                cardview:cardUseCompatPadding="true"
                android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                cardview:cardElevation="4dp"
                cardview:cardCornerRadius="5dp">
                <LinearLayout
                    android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                    android:layout_height="30dp"
                    android:gravity="top"
                    android:background="@drawable/banner"
                    android:orientation="vertical"
                    android:padding="8dp"/>
                <LinearLayout
                    android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:orientation="vertical"
                    android:padding="8dp">

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium"
                        android:textColor="#454545"
                        android:textSize="24sp"
                        android:textIsSelectable="true"
                        android:layout_marginTop="29sp"
                        android:textStyle="bold"
                        android:text="Google Developers Group"
                        android:id="@+id/textView1"
                        android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                        android:layout_marginLeft="5dp" />

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_marginTop="10sp"
                        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium"
                        android:textColor="#333333"
                        android:textIsSelectable="true"
                        android:text="Google Developer Group Minna (GDG Minna) is the first of its kind technical community or group for students and enthusiastic developers who are interested in Googles Developers technology; from Android, App Engine, Chrome, Google Cloud Platforms, to Products APIs like Youtube API, Maps API, Drive API and Google Calendar API.\n"
                        android:id="@+id/textView2"
                        android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                        android:layout_marginLeft="5dp" />

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium"
                        android:textColor="#333333"
                        android:textIsSelectable="true"
                        android:text="The Group is Managed by Volunteers. And we are always happy to accept new volunteers interested to be part of the organizational team.\n"
                        android:id="@+id/textView3"
                        android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                        android:layout_marginLeft="5dp" />

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium"
                        android:textColor="#333333"
                        android:textIsSelectable="true"
                        android:text="GDG Minna is located in Minna in the state capital of Niger State, Nigeria."
                        android:id="@+id/textView4"
                        android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                        android:layout_marginLeft="5dp" />

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:autoLink="web"
                        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium"
                        android:textColor="#333333"
                        android:textIsSelectable="true"
                        android:text="developers.google.com/groups"
                        android:id="@+id/textView5"
                        android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                        android:layout_marginLeft="5dp" />
                </LinearLayout>
            </android.support.v7.widget.CardView>

            <android.support.v7.widget.CardView
                android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                cardview:cardUseCompatPadding="true"
                android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                cardview:cardElevation="4dp"
                cardview:cardCornerRadius="5dp">
                <LinearLayout
                    android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                    android:layout_height="30dp"
                    android:gravity="top"
                    android:background="@drawable/banner"
                    android:orientation="vertical"
                    android:padding="8dp"/>
                <LinearLayout
                    android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:orientation="vertical"
                    android:padding="8dp">

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_marginTop="39sp"
                        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium"
                        android:textColor="#333333"
                        android:textIsSelectable="true"
                        android:text="A GDG is"
                        android:textSize="25sp"
                        android:textStyle="bold"
                        android:id="@+id/textView12"
                        android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                        android:layout_marginLeft="5dp" />

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium"
                        android:textColor="#333333"
                        android:textIsSelectable="true"
                        android:text="1. A place to learn about Google Technologies and Tools for developers.\n"
                        android:id="@+id/textView13"
                        android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                        android:layout_marginLeft="5dp" />

                    <TextView
                    android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium"
                    android:textColor="#333333"
                    android:textIsSelectable="true"
                    android:text="2. A place to see what local companies and developers are doing with these technologies.\n"
                    android:id="@+id/textView14"
                    android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                    android:layout_marginLeft="5dp" />

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium"
                        android:textColor="#333333"
                        android:textIsSelectable="true"
                        android:text="3. Focused on developers and educational technical content.\n"
                        android:id="@+id/textView15"
                        android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                        android:layout_marginLeft="5dp" />

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium"
                        android:textColor="#333333"
                        android:textIsSelectable="true"
                        android:text="4. Open to the public with a public membership.\n"
                        android:id="@+id/textView16"
                        android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                        android:layout_marginLeft="5dp" />

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium"
                        android:textColor="#333333"
                        android:textIsSelectable="true"
                        android:text="5. A place to meet cool and smart people in tech :)"
                        android:id="@+id/textView17"
                        android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                        android:layout_marginLeft="5dp" />

                </LinearLayout>
            </android.support.v7.widget.CardView>

            <android.support.v7.widget.CardView
                android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                cardview:cardUseCompatPadding="true"
                android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                cardview:cardElevation="4dp"
                cardview:cardCornerRadius="5dp">
                <LinearLayout
                    android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                    android:layout_height="30dp"
                    android:gravity="top"
                    android:background="@drawable/banner"
                    android:orientation="vertical"
                    android:padding="8dp"/>
                <LinearLayout
                    android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:orientation="vertical"
                    android:padding="8dp">

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_marginTop="39sp"
                        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium"
                        android:textColor="#333333"
                        android:textIsSelectable="true"
                        android:text="A GDG is NOT..."
                        android:textSize="25sp"
                        android:textStyle="bold"
                        android:id="@+id/textView6"
                        android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                        android:layout_marginLeft="5dp" />

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium"
                        android:textColor="#333333"
                        android:textIsSelectable="true"
                        android:text="1. Run by a corporation.\n"
                        android:id="@+id/textView7"
                        android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                        android:layout_marginLeft="5dp" />

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium"
                        android:textColor="#333333"
                        android:textIsSelectable="true"
                        android:text="2. A place to hear a very salesy pitch at any time.\n"
                        android:id="@+id/textView8"
                        android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                        android:layout_marginLeft="5dp" />

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium"
                        android:textColor="#333333"
                        android:textIsSelectable="true"
                        android:text="3. Focused on end users or consumer content.\n"
                        android:id="@+id/textView9"
                        android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                        android:layout_marginLeft="5dp" />

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium"
                        android:textColor="#333333"
                        android:textIsSelectable="true"
                        android:text="4. A closed group.\n"
                        android:id="@+id/textView10"
                        android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                        android:layout_marginLeft="5dp" />
                </LinearLayout>
            </android.support.v7.widget.CardView>

            <android.support.v7.widget.CardView
                android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                cardview:cardUseCompatPadding="true"
                android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                cardview:cardElevation="4dp"
                cardview:cardCornerRadius="5dp">
                <LinearLayout
                    android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:orientation="vertical"
                    android:padding="8dp">
                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="match_parent"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium"
                        android:textColor="#ffffff"
                        android:textIsSelectable="true"
                        android:gravity="center"
                        android:text="Our Mission"
                        android:background="#0095db"
                        android:textSize="25sp"
                        android:textStyle="bold"
                        android:id="@+id/textView20"
                        android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                        android:layout_marginLeft="5dp" />

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium"
                        android:textColor="#333333"
                        android:textIsSelectable="true"
                        android:text="To Train Technology Enthusiast as well as those Interested in Developing to Attain their Visions and Goals by Organizing events and Meet-Ups that Empowers them with Necessary Tools and Technology. Also, to encourage ready-made Developers to attain Heights by Creating Universal Solutions that Drives Change."
                        android:id="@+id/textView21"
                        android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                        android:layout_marginLeft="5dp" />

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="match_parent"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium"
                        android:textColor="#ffffff"
                        android:textIsSelectable="true"
                        android:gravity="center"
                        android:text="Our Vision"
                        android:background="#e50000"
                        android:textSize="25sp"
                        android:textStyle="bold"
                        android:id="@+id/textView22"
                        android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                        android:layout_marginLeft="5dp" />

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium"
                        android:textColor="#333333"
                        android:textIsSelectable="true"
                        android:text="To Empower Members to be Makers of Technology."
                        android:id="@+id/textView23"
                        android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                        android:layout_marginLeft="5dp" />

                </LinearLayout>
            </android.support.v7.widget.CardView>
        </LinearLayout>
    </ScrollView>
</LinearLayout>